**Description:** **: This code is a Python module that integrates Ollama (an AI model server) with a Flask web application. It defines a class called OllamaChat that handles interactions with the Ollama API, including listing available models with sorting and filtering, encoding images, creating test images, streaming chat responses, and managing conversation history. The module also sets up a Flask app to provide a web-based user interface for users to select models, input prompts, and view responses in real-time. The purpose is to create a local chat interface for AI models, supporting features like model selection, image processing, and streaming responses for a better user experience.

